OL,5, The RAC has accused petrol retailers of
OL,6, ripping off motorists by refusing to   
OL,7, pass on wholesale price cuts.          
OL,9,FThe motoring organisation said unleaded
OL,10,Fpetrol fell by 2p a litre, but should  
OL,11,Fhave come down by 12p.                 
OL,13,FIt estimated drivers were overcharged  
OL,14,Fby #5m a day in December as retailers  
OL,15,Fmade an average of 16p a litre on      
OL,16,Fpetrol instead of the normal 6p.       
OL,18,FThe Petrol Retailers Association       
OL,19,Fobjected, saying drivers were likely to
OL,20,Fhave benefited more than that.         
